        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780996469234" href="/book/show/36800752-the-truth-seeker-s-handbook">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2343861110" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4445624328981200078">Basically a self-help guide for people who are unlikely to benefit from it. It encourages you to consider other people’s perspectives, keep an open mind, accept the fact that your beliefs could be mistaken. If you’re willing to read this book then you probably don’t need to read it. If you’re someone who needs to improve, you’re probably too close-minded to pay attention to anything these people say.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


