<span id="freeTextContainer4392238330650169670">I just finished reading The Truth-Seeker’s Handbook: A Science-Based Guide. I can&apos;t express through words what I feel. This handbook changes everything. I always thought I was pretty good at making decisions until I realized what a rookie I am.<br/><br/>I was really surprised by how much this book helped me in my daily life seeking for truth. I consider The Truth-Seeker’s Handbook: A Science-Based Guide to be the best book I had ever read. Since I graduated college, I was faced with making important life </span>
  <span id="freeText4392238330650169670" style="display:none">I just finished reading The Truth-Seeker’s Handbook: A Science-Based Guide. I can't express through words what I feel. This handbook changes everything. I always thought I was pretty good at making decisions until I realized what a rookie I am.<br /><br />I was really surprised by how much this book helped me in my daily life seeking for truth. I consider The Truth-Seeker’s Handbook: A Science-Based Guide to be the best book I had ever read. Since I graduated college, I was faced with making important life decisions. Unfortunately, I made very few smart decisions. As I look back, I definitely could have changed it all with the help of this book.<br /><br />The "Strategies for Individual and Organizational Decision-Making" section was my favorite part of the book. Where it provides “Guidelines on Avoiding Disastrous Decisions”, it really helped me in making some big decisions in life. This book does a great job at making you look at your decisions from an objective viewpoint.<br /><br />I think I am more vulnerable to planning fallacy. I always have the tendency to underestimate the amount of time a project will take to complete. After reading this book I learned that I need to think about how long I usually have taken in the past to complete a project and break it down into smaller parts and consider how long each part will take. I would definitely recommend this book to anyone, especially people that have many big decisions ahead of them in the near future.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="4392238330650169670" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

