        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2480986571" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6527949763601804825">There&apos;s a lot of good summary here and good leads on citations to more scholarly research. However, the book itself probably doesn&apos;t need to exist in book form. It&apos;s really just a compilation of a bunch of (good) blog posts which, taken together, are often repetitive and (frankly) warrant copy-editing. That said, Tsipursky&apos;s Pro-Truth Pledge is an interesting concept.</span>
  <span id="freeText6527949763601804825" style="display:none">There's a lot of good summary here and good leads on citations to more scholarly research. However, the book itself probably doesn't need to exist in book form. It's really just a compilation of a bunch of (good) blog posts which, taken together, are often repetitive and (frankly) warrant copy-editing. That said, Tsipursky's Pro-Truth Pledge is an interesting concept.</span>
