        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3458972236" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16853773608838221697">This is an excellent book! It not only gives wonderful insights about how to think about truth and what gets in our way of accepting it, it also offers a variety of research-based tools for ensuring that our beliefs are aligned with reality. <br/><br/>With truth and fake news has become a hot topic dominating on social media, news headlines and conversations with friends and family members, it is very simple to allow our feelings towards one party or the other on the idea of truth to disregard the real po</span>
  <span id="freeText16853773608838221697" style="display:none">This is an excellent book! It not only gives wonderful insights about how to think about truth and what gets in our way of accepting it, it also offers a variety of research-based tools for ensuring that our beliefs are aligned with reality. <br /><br />With truth and fake news has become a hot topic dominating on social media, news headlines and conversations with friends and family members, it is very simple to allow our feelings towards one party or the other on the idea of truth to disregard the real position on the opposite party of the issue. This book is very helpful as it provides resources on effective decision-making. <br /><br />As a businesswoman, I find it hard to make decisions. Acknowledging cognitive biases, this book has provided a factual and scientific approach to everyday decisions. It’s a book worth your time reading and would highly recommend this book to anyone! </span>
  <a data-text-id="16853773608838221697" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

