<span id="freeTextContainer18391848182715325243">This is one of the best handbook I have read in this challenging times. The &quot;stay-at-home&quot; rule brought about by the COVID-19 pandemic has made me read this book and it&apos;s worth my time and money.<br/><br/>It&apos;s true to its title as a Science-based guide. The author has based his solutions to facts and reliable researches. It&apos;s a no non-sense handbook that will be a guide for small, medium, and big entrepreneurs - even those who are dreaming to become one. <br/><br/>I personally have biases on my decisions especially</span>
  <span id="freeText18391848182715325243" style="display:none">This is one of the best handbook I have read in this challenging times. The "stay-at-home" rule brought about by the COVID-19 pandemic has made me read this book and it's worth my time and money.<br /><br />It's true to its title as a Science-based guide. The author has based his solutions to facts and reliable researches. It's a no non-sense handbook that will be a guide for small, medium, and big entrepreneurs - even those who are dreaming to become one. <br /><br />I personally have biases on my decisions especially when it involves emotions on my part. But this book introduces to several factors to remove the biases and decide on the most logical and scientific approach. you have to read it to believe. </span>
