        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3282462890" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6991981614553604258">The Truth-Seeker&apos;s Handbook definitely comes handy for me. I may not be a big time businessman but I was able to learn a lot from the solutions being presented in this handbook, especially in the area of leadership and decision making. These 2 are vital for any businesses - big or small. <br/><br/>As an owner of a small enterprise, I struggle to make small decision every single day. Whether it&apos;s how to deal with tardiness to promoting an employee, everything has to be in place and carefully thought of. Th</span>
  <span id="freeText6991981614553604258" style="display:none">The Truth-Seeker's Handbook definitely comes handy for me. I may not be a big time businessman but I was able to learn a lot from the solutions being presented in this handbook, especially in the area of leadership and decision making. These 2 are vital for any businesses - big or small. <br /><br />As an owner of a small enterprise, I struggle to make small decision every single day. Whether it's how to deal with tardiness to promoting an employee, everything has to be in place and carefully thought of. The handbook has provided a factual, experience-based and scientific approach to every day issues. <br /><br />This is a worthwhile read. Highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6991981614553604258" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

